            <div class="bg-overlay"></div>
            <%= image_tag 'home/pillar-learn' %>
            <div class="text">LEARN</div>
          </div>
          <div class="pillar-inner">
            <p class="hidden-xs margin-bottom">iX is far from a typical classroom. We’re more of an <b>intense 4-week workshop</b>. The best way to learn is by working together and getting your hands dirty. 
            </p>
            <dl>
              <dt>The daily ritual:</dt>
              <dd>Expert instruction</dd>
              <dd>Collaborative learning</dd>
              <dd>Practice, practice, practice</dd>
            </dl>
